OL,6,FAled Williams has been documenting his
OL,7,Fexperiences since December using
OL,8,FTransport for Wales trains travelling
OL,9,Ffrom the town to Bridgend, Cardiff and
OL,10,FNewport.
OL,12,FDuring his journeys, he says the,
OL,13,Fovercrowded, he has missed connections
OL,14,Fand some have been cancelled
OL,15,Faltogether without alternative
OL,16,Ftransport arrangements.
OL,18,FAccording to Aled, the local service
OL,19,Fis "unreliable."
