OL,6,F"Sometimes, you will be waiting on the
OL,7,Fplatform, and then there will be an
OL,8,Fannouncement saying (the train) is
OL,9,Flate, and then later, and then later -
OL,10,Fand then, it doesn't come at all. But
OL,11,Fthere will be no prior warning that it
OL,12,Fwon't be coming, and there's only one
OL,13,Ftrain an hour.
OL,15,F"It is happening more and more often
OL,16,Frecently" he said. "But it is harder
OL,17,Fto come back than to go somewhere."
