OL,6,FCurrently the train from Maesteg to
OL,7,FCardiff leaves every hour during the
OL,8,Fweek. There are means to catch the bus
OL,9,Fduring the week; however, following
OL,10,Fcuts, there are no buses from Bridgend
OL,11,Fto Maesteg after 5.30pm.
OL,13,FMany regular commuters told Y Byd ar
OL,14,FBedwar that the train often terminates
OL,15,Fearly, without warning, in Tondu and
OL,16,Fdoes not reach Maesteg.
