OL,6,FThis is because there is a single
OL,7,Ftrack connecting Tondu and Maesteg
OL,8,Fstations, therefore there is no way
OL,9,Ffor two trains to pass if one is
OL,10,Frunning late.
OL,12,FAled Williams said that the situation
OL,13,Fis not good enough for commuters that
OL,14,Fare eager to get home.
OL,16,F"On the train, it would take ten
OL,17,Fminutes, a quarter of an hour. There's
OL,18,Fno means to walk," he said.
