OL,6,FAlthough this is a regular issue for
OL,7,FAled, he says taking a car is not an
OL,8,Foption for him.
OL,10,F"There's a lot of people here that
OL,11,Fdon't drive, it's a fairly poor area."
OL,13,FOne in every five households in
OL,14,FBridgend do not own a car or van, and
OL,15,Faccording to the Welsh Index of
OL,16,FMultiple Deprivation, Maesteg is
OL,17,Fconsidered a built-up area with deep-
OL,18,Frooted deprivation.
OL,20,F"I know that I won't be able to afford
OL,21,Fa car or lessons to be honest.
