OL,6,F"I am reliant on this service, and it
OL,7,Fdoes not work - they're getting worse
OL,8,Fand worse."
OL,10,FAccording to a YouGov opinion poll,
OL,11,Fcommissioned by ITV Cymru Wales in
OL,12,FDecember 2023, out of 1,000
OL,13,Frespondents who were asked what they
OL,14,Fthink about the rail service provided
OL,15,Fby Transport for Wales, 45% said that
OL,16,Fthey believed it was unreliable.
OL,18,FAs someone who has missed appointments
OL,19,Fdue to local services, Aled has had to
OL,20,Fplan more carefully for important
OL,21,Fjourneys.
