OL,6,F"If I have an appointment in Bridgend,
OL,7,For something like that, I tend to
OL,8,Fleave an hour earlier, just to make
OL,9,Fsure that I can get there at all.
OL,11,F"It impacts people when they are
OL,12,Ftrying to find a job.
