OL,6,FIn an interview, Gethin Jones, Public
OL,7,FAffairs Manager at Transport for
OL,8,FWales, said that the "concerns were
OL,9,Fvery valid."
OL,11,F"We know that there is room to improve
OL,12,Fservices within this area particularly
OL,13,F- and that's why we have invested,
OL,14,Fsince 2018, #800 million into a new
OL,15,Ffleet of trains, and to improve
OL,16,Fstations."
OL,18,FThe company announced that new Class
OL,19,F197 trains will be running on the line
OL,20,Ffrom the 19 February.
